    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the saline rinse and it didnt really do much... its just making me feel more stuffy. i know it's not ideal but i really just need some relief so i can function tomorrow. is there like a specific dose of pseudoephedrine that is considered safe in the second trimester? maybe a lower dose would be okay?",
